{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, the USA and China demonstrated the strongest collaboration, appearing in 52 articles.",
    "This was followed by collaborations between China and the UK (18), South Korea and the USA (14), and the UK and the USA (12).",
    "In Fig. 4b, collaborations among 10 countries/regions are showcased, featuring collaborative frequencies ranging from 6 to 7.",
    "Of the 10 countries/ regions, 4 are from Asia (pink nodes) and 3 are from Europe (green nodes).",
    "The collaboration among them is close as witnessed by three collaborative clusters: 2) China and Hong Kong, 2) Italy, the UK, and Germany, and 3) Saudi Arabia and Pakistan."
  ]
}